{"tid":2303686,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官指防暴口供不合理 少年脫襲警罪  庭外寄語手足「唔好放棄」","createTime":"2020-11-28T07:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T07:47:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9f8dd13585e8691d96b2262327da4bd368ad67b8","tid":2303686,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:02:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/LMA2ZFZ5LVF4XCFAGGVYP5XWLM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2FLMA2ZFZ5LVF4XCFAGGVYP5XWLM%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CiF8jviwHHlsaTD6zKFHFMM%3D&h=91fa4ab5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201128%2FLMA2ZFZ5LVF4XCFAGGVYP5XWLM%2F&h=1de8c54c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201128/LMA2ZFZ5LVF4XCFAGGVYP5XWLM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官指防暴口供不合理 少年脫襲警罪 <br />\n庭外寄語手足「唔好放棄」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VpsuGNbAzDmvvYyDNBpOLgTpUCE=/2624x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J5NXR3FKVNERNCYGDM3Y6N2T2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVpsuGNbAzDmvvYyDNBpOLgTpUCE%3D%2F2624x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ5NXR3FKVNERNCYGDM3Y6N2T2M.jpg&h=7978e92f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■去年聖誕有市民發起到德福廣場「和你Shop」，防暴警到場拘捕多人。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】市民去年聖誕發起到不同商場「和你Shop」，其中在九龍灣德福廣場，一名17歲男學生被指逃走時以肩撞防暴警，導致警員後退一步。案件昨裁決，裁判官梁少玲指涉案警作供內容不準確，不排除被告逃跑時未能預計會遭警員阻擋去路，從而無可避免地撞到其盾牌，認為被告沒意圖襲警，裁定他襲警罪名不成立。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：辯方倡警司警誡 律政司企硬<br />\n<br />\n梁官宣判一刻，公眾席上響起一片掌聲，17歲陳姓被告的母親掩面到庭外抽泣。被告散庭後獲支持者道賀，他向記者寄語手足「唔好放棄」。控罪指被告去年12月25日在九龍灣德福廣場一期1樓Fancl外襲擊警員7100陳俊傑（譯音）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n書面供詞無提盾被撞<br />\n<br />\n梁官分析審訊證供時質疑兩名涉案警員的說法，並明言會對他們的證供給予較輕比重。根據案中證供及片段，被告案發時在奔逃，有路便走，原本無人阻擋去路，惟陳突然擋在被告前面攔截。梁官指由於被告正在奔跑，未能及時減速，因此與陳的盾牌發生碰撞。梁官認為，不排除被告未能預計逃走途中遇上警員突然改變位置，因而造成無可避免的碰撞，裁定被告沒意圖襲擊陳。<br />\n<br />\n陳在庭上供稱，被告以右膊撞到盾牌再壓向其胸，令他倒退半步。梁官指被告撞向他的盾牌是關鍵一幕，但陳沒有在記事冊及書面供詞中記錄此事，只是報稱胸口被撞。陳出庭作供時就此解釋稱，胸口較盾牌重要。梁官質疑其說法既奇怪，亦不合理。梁官又指出，陳當時連同身上裝備，重量約共90公斤，他也同意被告身形瘦小，片段亦看不到陳警員被撞後踏後半步。<br />\n<br />\n梁官亦質疑。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC1055/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/yUmFiso0ZTso1YsqSjfujg2AXrc=/1575x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/USIEARIVUBFMNB2NZXRKIEPPOU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FyUmFiso0ZTso1YsqSjfujg2AXrc%3D%2F1575x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUSIEARIVUBFMNB2NZXRKIEPPOU.jpg&h=33a0fdec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員24710<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VZVFeXAZmp9uo0kLGYsT3_xvVGA=/1575x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2P37CWOFTBAYFAWT74W2LCTYZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVZVFeXAZmp9uo0kLGYsT3_xvVGA%3D%2F1575x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2P37CWOFTBAYFAWT74W2LCTYZU.jpg&h=aba42f4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員7100"},{"pid":"31f8fb44f80dc8d59081ce75d21f220c98bb497d","tid":2303686,"uid":214635,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:05:36.000Z","msg":"襲警呢條罪幾時先廢咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最多告虐畜算啦"},{"pid":"930882edeb6605b53644b0f87dec12b3fabf75df","tid":2303686,"uid":100697,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T07:12:41.000Z","msg":"大波驊: 上訴 <br />\n再唔成功就大人釋法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a86840684164a87